snippet.textDisplay:
shuno akdom tension korbha na amar jonnhe.Aije tumar ai poristthiti ta aksomoy kichu month er jonnhe amar o chilo mone ache?songgho diye karapp somoy ghulo katai uthchi,kar ki aukaat dekai chadchi… hoyto tumi tkn amar sath e chilaa.akn hoyto tumar khetree ami nai.buji ami hoyto tumar r amar poribsh akh na…buji ami bujccho…Tension korio na somoy naw pera nai jotto din/bocor laghe kar ki aukaat dekai chadbhe…strong thakbe…bujccho…bissash koro oije oi “Norpurush” ttar sath e heshe kotah bolcho bhableo amar gaa shiyyo dei…jana ache kmn r kotai r kisher upoor acho…ami bissash rakih…amar uporo bissash ta rakio💜

aar insha Allah amar ai koiakta mash,aksomoy jara piche kotah bolche tader akn hath ei mutoi niye khela korchi pera nai…amar tekeo tader akn pera hoy geche ai poribesh teke ber howar jonnhe…prottekh ta kutinati tara janhe ai “শকূন" er beppare…
tader sath e akno ai “শকূন" der sath e jogajogh nei…bhabo tho profession life niye matobbhori kolaiche ai obostta…jkn somoy hobe tkn personal bisoy ghulote matabbhori kolabe bujtecho ki obostta kore chadbho…
Oije 3 bangbbhe bolchi alhamdulillah 3ottukh bangbhe na…daro 1 Moto jabe insha Allah…kotah hoy geche…pera nio bujccho.Strong thakio💜
